=== Overview

serialport is used to configure serial port.

==== Options

--- ttyMAX0
specify ttyMAX0 as serial port.

--- ttyS0
specify ttyS0 as serial port.

--- ttyS1
specify ttyS1 as serial port.

--- ttyS2
specify ttyS2 as serial port.

--- ttyUSB0
specify ttyUSB0 as serial port.

--- none
empty dir.

--- default
when not explicitly selected in mixin spec file, the default option will be used.
It links none option.


